Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I'm on Page 08 of Mamma MRI
When I select the radio button 'Bone lesion'
Then 'Findings' dropdown is enabled
When I select 'Rib' from Findings dropdown menu
Then 'Add new finding' button is enabled
And 'C 1' checkbox is enabled
And 'C 2' checkbox is enabled
And 'C 3' checkbox is enabled
And 'C 4' checkbox is enabled
And 'C 5' checkbox is enabled
And 'C 6' checkbox is enabled
And 'C 7' checkbox is enabled
And 'C 8' checkbox is enabled
And 'C 9' checkbox is enabled
And 'C 10' checkbox is enabled
And 'C 11' checkbox is enabled
And 'C 12' checkbox is enabled
And 'Max. Diameter' input field is enabled
And 'Type of lesion' dropdown menu is enabled
When I select 'C 1' checkbox
Then 'Right' radio button is enabled
And 'Left' radio button is enabled
When When I select 'C 2' checkbox
Then 'Right' radio button is disabled
And 'Left' radio button is disabled.
